"1216","investment is waived if you make regular investments weekly,"
"1217","semi monthly, or monthly through automatic deductions through"
"1218","your bank checking or savings account. Currently, Putnam is"
"1219","waiving the minimum, but reserves the right to reject initial"
"1220","investments under the minimum."
